Package com.codecool.butler.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Dummy
    Dummy class responsible for populating a database with dummy datas for test purposes.
    Item
    In Item instances you can store every physical item by their name.
    Message
    Message store every message send to the application by the users.
    MessageType
    MassageType instances are type(or category) attachments for Message instances.
    Stock
    Stock class instances store the quantity of every Item instances.
    StockType
    StockType instances are type(or category) attachments for Stock instances.
    Tag
    Tag class instances responsible for categorizing everything in the application.
    TagType
    TagType instances are type(or category) attachments for Tag instances.
    User
    User instances collects every data for our users, like their contacts, inventory, messages, etc.
